The '''{{Path|/usr/portage/profiles}}''' directory contains global Gentoo profiles that are controlled by the developers. One of them needs to be [[Profile#Change profile|selected as the system profile]]. To override these settings, use the files in {{Path|[[:/etc/portage|/etc/portage/]]}}.

